[I] The Cinnamon Desktop

[T] Cinnamon is a Linux desktop that provides advanced innovative features and
[T] a traditional user experience. The desktop layout is similar to GNOME 2
[T] with underlying technology forked from the GNOME Shell. Cinnamon makes
[T] users feel at home with an easy-to-use and comfortable desktop experience.

[U] https://github.com/linuxmint/cinnamon

